Package: indi-fli
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libindi1, libfli1 (>= 1.8)
Description: INDI FLI CCD & Focuser Driver.
 .
 This driver is compatible with any INDI client such as KStars or Xephem.

Package: indi-fli-dbg
Priority: extra
Section: debug
Architecture: any
Depends: indi-fli (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: INDI FLI CCD & Focuser Driver.
 .
 This driver is compatible with any INDI client such as KStars or Xephem.
 This package contains the debug symbols for the this driver, useful to investigate problems in INDI.

